title: 76. How To Master The Moment
itunes:title: 76. How To Master The Moment
description: You do not have to be miserable all the time to be excellent. The highest achievers in the world are able to put aside all distractions and be present in the moment. On today's episode, Andy shares the skill you must master in order to be more effective and get an edge over the competition.
